opag (0.7.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release:
    - Code which can be used in programs with Native Language Support can
      be generated.
    - No non-ASCII characters appear in code examples in the manual page,
      even if viewed in non-ASCII locales.
  * Convert to building with cdbs.

 -- Martin Dickopp <martin-opag@zero-based.org>  Sun, 26 Sep 2004 14:48:17 +0200

